dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Outagamie County, WI 2021
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right-of-Ways (ROW) for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2021. [ROW: This is a polygon feature class representing the right of way boundaries within Outagamie County]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
